<!-- Ignore Unknown Tag names such as Header  -->
<!-- Output contents of tags at all times (ie Name, ',' in Field, etc.	-->
<!-- Try to implement xml pathing for location field so things like root/Documents/Document[2]/Name work-->
<Header>Name,Date,PageCount</Header>
<Repeater special="_File">
	<Repeater location="root/Documents/Document">
		<Field special="_FileName"/>,<Field location="root/ClientInfo/ShippedDate"/>,<Field location="root/Documents/Document/PageCount"/>
	</Repeater>
</Repeater>
<Space/>
<Total>,,<Field location="root/Documents/Document/PageCount"/></Total>

Example Input: textSchema.xml, C:\Dev\CSVReportGenerator\BasicTestFolder
Expected Output:
____________________________

Name,Date,PageCount
xmlFile1.xml,2025/01/01,17
xmlFile1.xml,2025/01/02,30
xmlFile2.xml,2025/02/01,5
xmlFile2.xml,2025/02/04,2
xmlFile3.xml,2025/02/07,11

,,65
______________________________
Outputs '' if nothing found ie

xmlFile1.xml,,17

Main Tags - Repeater, Field, Total, Space
Repeater - Attempts to repeat itself for every instance of special or location
Field - Attempt to output itself based on contents of special or location
Total - Attempt to total itself based on contents or location
Space - Insert blank line intentionally

location - XMLPath to use
special - alternative to XMLPath for unique purposes defined by application
	_File - used for looping on files
	_FileName - used to retrieve filename specifically, could also be used like File.